description: “Every Road Leads to Good Eats” and this is certainly true when The Cleveland Corned Beef Company is on the streets.  Donald & Lisa Dorsey (a cool Ohio couple) are serving Phoenix a delicious glimpse into the flavorful world of the East Coast with their tasty selection of Cleveland creations. Their specialities include Corned Beef Hoagies, Italian Sausage Dogs (Cleveland-style, topped with homemade french fries and coleslaw), BBQ Beef Brisket, and much more. Whether you’re hungry for lunch or planning your next event, The Cleveland Corned Beef Company is here and ready to accommodate all your needs.
name: The Cleveland Corned Beef Company
